                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.512/1217</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Representative <persName type="from"
                            >Rodgers</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico City</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-06-03T18:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 3, 1916, 6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>114. In reply to Department’s 116 June 5, [2] 5 p.m. Fee as stated prescribed;,
                    declared necessary for supervision in order to protect public. This action
                    indicated in my mail despatch No. 57.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Rodgers</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
